	    +---------------------------------------+
	    | Contenedor (display: flex)              |
	    |        justify-content: center         |
	    |        align-items: center            |
	    |        height: 100vh                  |
	    |    +-----------------------+          |
	    |    | Item centrado                    |
	    |    +-----------------------+          |
	    +---------------------------------------+
	    ```enduml```
	    
	    **Ejemplo 2: Diseño de barra de navegación**
	    
	    ```startuml```
	    +--------------------------------------------------+
	    | Nav (display: flex)                               |
	    | justify-content: space-between                   |
	    | background-color: darkblue                       |
	    |  +-------+                                      |
	    |  | Link  |                                      |
	    |  |   1   |                                      |
	    |  +-------+                                      |
	    |  +-------+                                      |
	    |  | Link  |                                      |
	    |  |   2   |                                      |
	    |  +-------+                                      |
	    |  +-------+
	    
	    ```startuml```
	    | | Link  |                                      |
	    |  |   3   |                                      |
	    |  +-------+                                      |
	    +--------------------------------------------------+
	    ```enduml```
	    
	    **Ejemplo 3: Tarjetas con altura y ancho iguales**
	    
	    ```startuml```
	    +--------------------------------------------------+
	    | Contenedor (display: flex)                       |
	    | flex-wrap: wrap                                  |
	    | justify-content: center                         |
	    | +-------------------+ +-------------------+      |
	    | | Card              | | Card               |      |
	    | | 1                   | | 2                  |      |
	    | +-------------------+ +-------------------+      |
	    | +-------------------+ +-------------------+      |
	    | | Card              | | Card              |      |
	    | | 3                   | | 4                  |      |
	    | +-------------------+ +-------------------+      |
	    +--------------------------------------------------+
	    ```enduml```
	    
	    **Ejemplo 4: Diseño de pie de página con distribución espacial**
	    
	    ```startuml```
	    +---------------------------------------------------+
	    | Footer (display: flex)                             |
	    | justify-content: space-around                     |
	    | background-color: black                            |
	    | +--------+ +--------+ +--------+ +--------+      |
	    | | Div     | | Div     | | Div     | | Div     |      |
	    | +--------+ +--------+ +--------+ +--------+      |
	    +---------------------------------------------------+
	    ```enduml```
	    
	    **Ejemplo 5: Columna de igual altura en diseño de tres columnas**
	    
	    ```startuml```
	    +---------------------------------------------------+
	    | Contenedor (display: flex)                         |
	    | +-------------+ +-------------+ +-------------+      |
	    | | Column 1     | | Column 2     | | Column 3     |      |
	    | +-------------+ +-------------+ +-------------+      |
	    +---------------------------------------------------+
	    ```enduml```
	    
	    Estos ejemplos prácticos demuestran cómo Flexbox puede utilizarse para crear diseños flexibles y adaptables para diversas aplicaciones.
	    
